emporal, J-L. (1985). Rapport Final d'Activités dans le Parc National Manovo-Gounda-St Floris. Rapport du projet. Fonds d'Aide et Coopération. * UNESCO World Heritage Committee (1997). Report on the 20th Session of the World Heritage Committee, Paris. * UNESCO World Heritage Committee (1998). Report on the 21st Session of the World Heritage Committee, Paris. * UNESCO World Heritage Committee (2001). Report on the 24th Session of the World Heritage Committee, Paris. * UNESCO World Heritage Committee (2002). Report on the 25th Session of the World Heritage Committee, Paris
